	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f102323247532729><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=12393&mid=102323247532729>Why some..</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=12393&mid=102323247532729#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=149274><span id= >Xeonic</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>121 posts</td></tr>
